data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Nestled in the heart of a gated community, 1109 Park Ridge Cir. is a captivating townhouse that offers a perfect blend of elegance, convenience, and security. This 3-bedroom, 2-full bath, and 1-half bath residence is a haven of modern living, equipped with an array of amenities that make it the ideal place to call home. As you enter this meticulously maintained townhouse, you're greeted with a spacious and airy living room/dining room combo that boasts contemporary design and an abundance of natural light.  The custom designed home also has an electric fireplace with backlighting that can be changed to suit your mood.  The interior features are thoughtfully selected and include ceiling fans, a master bedroom on the second floor, custom made solid surface counters, solid wood cabinets, offering a harmonious fusion of style and functionality. The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, equipped with a range of appliances, including a dishwasher, disposal, dryer, microwave, and refrigerator. This ensures that cooking and entertaining in this space is a delightful experience, and the solid wood cabinets and solid surface counters add an elegant touch to your culinary endeavors.  Not to forget the house has electric shades throughout the home. The private patio is perfect for your morning coffee, or even better, utilizing the balcony and enjoying the view!  Safety and security are paramount in this residence, which is located within a gated community and features not only controlled access but also around-the-clock security personnel for your peace of mind. Additionally, a fire alarm system is in place to provide further safety measures. The community itself offers a range of enticing amenities, including a sparkling pool, a perfect spot for relaxation and recreation, and additional security measures with a guarded gate, ensuring that residents enjoy a tranquil and secure living environment. 1109 Park Ridge Cir. represents the best of Florida living, offering a perfect combination of luxurious interior features and a welcoming community with top-notch security. With its elegant design, modern appliances, and serene surroundings, this townhouse invites you to experience the epitome of comfort and convenience in beautiful Kissimmee, FL. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home or to use as a short-term rental.  All furnishings included!
